3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4782.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Shissarbane Weapon Spoiler</span><hr size=1> Well since no one is posting what is needed for Shissarbane weapons, I will.  <br><br>1) You need one of the weapons wielded by the elite Shissars or similar weapons.  They are the easy part, and no need to really camp these<br><br>2) You need Green metal from the mines in Ssra.  They drop off named skeletons, and need 2 pretty solid groups to keep the caverns cleared (one group is enough, just won't keep all the PHs cleared as fast).  <br><br>3) Combine the weapon and the Green metal in the forge outside the mines.  You don't need any blacksmithing skill, 0 works just fine.  You get a corrupted shissar weapon of the type you combined. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvaslin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vaslin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Head Safehouse Admin</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/23/02 7:38:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4782.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shissarbane Weapon Spoiler</span><hr size=1> Thanks for confirming the recipe.  I've heard all the ingredients before, but never the 0 skill combine in the forge. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uskrilmo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Skrilmo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/23/02 8:29:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4782.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shissarbane We